## Summary
The Amplitude Experiment Ruby SDK provides both remote and local evaluation capabilities for feature flags, with support for user targeting, cohort targeting, and automatic assignment tracking. It includes configuration options for timeouts, retries, and EU data center compliance, along with utilities for handling Amplitude cookies.

